<div class="p-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-blue-400 uppercase">Neural Personality Config</h1>
    
    <form action="/admin/vastur/update" method="POST" class="max-w-3xl space-y-6">
        <div class="space-y-2">
            <label class="text-blue-300">AI Personality Name</label>
            <input type="text" name="aiName" value="DevCORE - AI" class="w-full bg-slate-900 p-3 rounded border border-blue-700 outline-none focus:border-blue-400">
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-2">
            <label class="text-blue-300">System Instruction (Persona)</label>
            <textarea name="persona" rows="8" class="w-full bg-slate-900 p-3 rounded border border-blue-700 outline-none focus:border-blue-400" 
            placeholder="Contoh: Kamu adalah DevCORE, asisten cerdas milik XdpzQ yang ahli dalam cyber security..."></textarea>
        </div>

        <div class="p-4 bg-blue-900/20 border-l-4 border-blue-500 text-xs italic">
            Note: Perubahan persona akan langsung mempengaruhi respons AI pada sesi berikutnya secara real-time.
        </div>

        <button class="bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-400 text-white font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-lg transition-all shadow-lg shadow-blue-900/50">
            SAVE NEURAL CORE
        </button>
    </form>
</div>
